Writing union types as X | Y is the feature of python 3.10, actually we should avoiding using it to ensure the compatibility. We will fix this in the future version, you can also submit a PR to fix this if you like.

You can fix it now by the folllowing methods:

- update your python to 3.10

or

- remove "-> Session|None" to avoid using this feature in codes and recompile py-client module in iotdb
